== FOR YOUR PARTNER OR SUPPORT PERSON

Labor can last 24+ hours. Your support person needs supplies too.

=== Essentials
- _Change of clothes_ - At least one full outfit, possibly two
- _Toiletries_ - Toothbrush, deodorant, etc.
- _Phone charger_ - Their own, don't share
- _Comfortable shoes_ - They'll be on their feet providing support

=== Food Situation
Your partner can eat when you can't (if you're restricted). They should:
- _Pack substantial snacks_ - Nuts, protein bars, dried fruit, crackers
- _Bring cash or card_ - For cafeteria and vending machines
- _Know the hospital food options_ - Cafeteria hours, nearby restaurants, delivery options

=== Entertainment
- _Book, tablet, or downloaded shows_ - For early labor downtime
- _Laptop_ - If they need to work remotely (labor takes a while sometimes)

=== Support Items
- _Bathing suit_ - If you're using a labor tub, your partner may want to get in with you
- _Camera_ - If you want photos beyond phone quality
- _Watch with a second hand_ - For timing contractions if phone dies

